  <abstract>This report explains the causes of homelessness among children; makes clear its cost to children, families and society; proposes an agenda to eradicate homelessness; summarizes many studies about who homeless families are, why they become homeless, and how homelessness hurts children and families; and suggests steps to help communities and policy makers prevent homelessness and address the needs of homeless families</abstract>
